  CONTAINER
    HEADER
      "Resting on top is"
   VERB examine
     DOES ONLY
       LIST THIS.
   END VERB.
   VERB put_in
     WHEN obj2
       CHECK
         "That isn't something you can put anything ""in""."
   END VERB.
