Every CLOSEABLE Isa OBJECT
  OPAQUE CONTAINER
    HEADER
      "It contains"
  IS OPENABLE.
  VERB open DOES AFTER
    MAKE THIS NOT OPAQUE.
    LIST THIS.
  END VERB.
  VERB close DOES AFTER
    MAKE THIS OPAQUE.
  END VERB.
END EVERY.
