EVERY Door Isa OBJECT
  NAME door
  HAS otherside Door.
  IS OPENABLE.
  DESCRIPTION
  VERB open
    DOES AFTER
      MAKE otherside OF THIS open.
  END VERB.
  VERB close
    DOES AFTER
      MAKE otherside OF THIS NOT open.
  END VERB.
